Murray & Roberts Zimbabwe Appoints Mangoma as CEO, News Reports

-- B y   B r i a n   L a t h a m
-- 
2011-07-13T07:44:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-13/murray-roberts-zimbabwe-appoints-mangoma-as-ceo-news-reports.html
Murray & Roberts Holding ( Zimbabwe )
Ltd. appointed Stewart Mangoma as chief executive officer, the
 Daily News  reported, without saying where it got the
information.  Mangoma, who replaces Canada Malunga, was previously group
finance director at the Harare-based construction company, which
he joined in 2006, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brian Latham in Johannesburg on  at
 blatham@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at   asguazzin@bloomberg.net  